The files in web/ is a web app, the viewer of bgm-archive.

It uses Preact and Preact-router. The main web component library is primereact.

The important files you will work on are:

```
web/main.tsx : the bundle entrypoint, importing page components and mount at router.
web/pages : the page components
web/src : everything else
```

The web viewer is based on the backend API in the same repository, whose OpenAPI definition can be found at `web/openapi.json`